            Fusion CMS (Enterprise and Cloud editions), and the Oxygen XML Author Desktop.</p>
        <p>The <b>Content Fusion Enterprise CMS</b> (installed on the client's premise) and
                <b>Oxygen XML Author Desktop</b> are available for purchase.</p>
